<li><a href="/wiki/XM_Radio" title="XM Radio" class="mw-redirect">XM Radio</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Sirius_Satellite_Radio" title="Sirius Satellite Radio">Sirius Satellite Radio</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wireless_LAN" title="Wireless LAN">Wireless LANs</a></li>
