<li>Wunsch, A. David "<i><a href="http://www.mercurians.org/nov98/misreading.html" class="external text" title="http://www.mercurians.org/nov98/misreading.html" rel="nofollow">Misreading the Supreme Court: A Puzzling Chapter in the History of Radio</a></i>". Mercurians.org.</li>
</ul>
</div>
